OL,3,CSister of Ruth Perry says delays to
OL,4,COfsted reforms 'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FThe sister of Reading headteacher Ruth
OL,7,FPerry has said that delays to Ofsted
OL,8,Freforms are "putting more lives at
OL,9,Frisk".
OL,11,FProfessor Julia Waters spoke at the
OL,12,Fannual conference of the National
OL,13,FEducation Union in Bournemouth on
OL,14,FFriday 5 April.
OL,16,FRuth Perry took her own life after an
OL,17,FOfsted report downgraded Caversham
OL,18,FPrimary School from its highest rating
OL,19,Fto its lowest over safeguarding
OL,20,Fconcerns.
