OL,3,CSister of Ruth Perry says delays to
OL,4,COfsted reforms 'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FShe said: "How many more children will
OL,7,Flose another dedicated headteacher to
OL,8,Fa forced resignation, a nervous
OL,9,Fbreakdown, or worse?
OL,11,F"Delays and obfuscation put more lives
OL,12,Fat risk. It's not acceptable to play
OL,13,Fpolitics with people's wellbeing."
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, delegates at the NEU
OL,16,Fconference voted for a "public facing"
OL,17,Fcampaign, calling for Ofsted to be
OL,18,Fabolished, to be launched by the union.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
