OL,6,FBut Prof Waters called on the NEU to
OL,7,Fstop campaigning to abolish Ofsted and
OL,8,Fto instead put "considerable energy"
OL,9,Finto the opportunity for real change
OL,10,Fby working together to make the
OL,11,Finspection system "better and kinder".
OL,13,FIn her speech, Prof Waters said:
OL,14,F"Let's not settle for half-measures.
OL,15,FSome changes have already been made.
