OL,6,F"But more changes are needed to ensure
OL,7,Fthat no other teacher or headteacher
OL,8,Ffeels pushed to the intolerable depths
OL,9,Fof despair by a system that is meant
OL,10,Fto 'raise standards' and 'improve
OL,11,Flives'."
OL,13,FVideo footage of Mrs Perry, who was an
OL,14,FNEU member, was shown at the union's
OL,15,Fconference during the speech by her
OL,16,Fsister.
