OL,3,CSister of Ruth Perry says delays to
OL,4,COfsted reforms 'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FIn the video, which was recorded
OL,7,Fduring the Covid-19 pandemic, Mrs
OL,8,FPerry told her Caversham Primary
OL,9,FSchool pupils: "Talk to the people you
OL,10,Flove, be kind to each other, be
OL,11,Fhopeful, take care of yourselves and
OL,12,Feach other."
OL,14,FProf Waters said: "As Ruth said, be
OL,15,Fkind. Show compassion. Talk to each
OL,16,Fother. Be hopeful that change is
OL,17,Fcoming."
