OL,3,CSister of Ruth Perry says delays to
OL,4,COfsted reforms 'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,FAddressing teachers and school leaders
OL,7,Facross the country, Prof Waters said:
OL,8,F"If you feel anything like how Ruth
OL,9,Ffelt, I really feel for you.
OL,11,F"She saw everything she had stood for
OL,12,Fin her career and her community
OL,13,Fdestroyed in a moment by an unfair
OL,14,FOfsted decision. She was offered no
OL,15,Fway out.
OL,17,F"But let me tell you, suicide is
OL,18,Falways a terrible, wrong-headed
OL,19,Foption. Ending her own life was the
OL,20,Fworst thing Ruth could possibly have
OL,21,Fdone.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
