OL,3,CSister of Ruth Perry says delays to
OL,4,COfsted reforms 'putting lives at risk'
OL,6,F"That desperate act devastated our
OL,7,Ffamily, her colleagues, the hundreds
OL,8,Fof her pupils and a whole community in
OL,9,FCaversham and beyond. We shall all
OL,10,Flive with the devastation of Ruth's
OL,11,Fappalling, preventable death for the
OL,12,Frest of our lives.
OL,14,F"So if you are having thoughts about
OL,15,Fending your own life ` please, think
OL,16,Fagain. Get help."
OL,18,FAt the start of the year, Ofsted
OL,19,Finspections were paused in England to
OL,20,Fensure inspectors were given mental
OL,21,Fhealth awareness training.
